{| class="wikitable floatright"
|+ Prisoner's dilemma payoff matrix
! {{diagonal split header|A|B}}
! B stays<br />silent
! B<br />betrays
|-
! A stays<br />silent
| {{diagonal split header|-1|-1|transparent}}
